data.description: Fantastic bi-level home on a mature lot convenient to Powers or Academy Blvd for commutes in every direction. A block down the street enjoy Penrose park and Homestead Trail with miles of walking paths/trails to connect the community. Newer kitchen with custom cabinets, stainless appliances, and granite counters. Bonus sun room steps down from kitchen.. great for horticulture, game table, or entertainment! The main living spaces are tile or laminate flooring, with bedrooms and lower family having carpet. Enjoy a wall-length brick fireplace to keep the lower level cozy during those chilly days and nights. Out through the sun room or garage to a tremendous back yard with 2 patios (8x38 + 10x13) and a massive firepit, plus tremendous shed. Both active solar panel system and passive solar sunroom. Welcome home to Raintree, in the Village 7 area.
